window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>DELUXE EDITION, featuring a never-before-heard bonus chapter!<br> </b><br> <b>From </b><b><i>New York Times</i></b><b> bestselling author J.T. Geissinger comes </b><b><i>Ruthless Creatures</i></b><b>, a scorchingly hot mafia romance about two people bound together by a debt that must be collected. No matter the cost. This program features multicast narration.</b><br> <br> Five years ago, my fiancé disappeared. He left me with a wedding dress I’d never wear. Left me with the kind of scars that can’t be healed. The man I built my future on vanished like a ghost. All that remained were my broken heart and a million unanswered questions.<br> <br> Until a mysterious stranger arrives in town.<br> <br> Tall, dark, and dangerous, Kage is as full of secrets as he is sex appeal. Though I know he’s hiding something, I’m drawn to him like a moth to flame. Heat crackles between us with every look, desire flares into passion, and I fall hard, helpless to resist.<br> <br> But then I discover he’s been sent to collect on an unpaid debt from my missing fiancé....<br> <br> And that debt is me.<br> <br> <b>Queens and Monsters Listening Order:</b><br> Ruthless Creatures<br> Carnal Urges<br> Savage Hearts<br> Brutal Vows<br> <br> <b>A Macmillan Audio production from Tor Books.</b></p>"; 
